pageContext.claim: “The other thing is, you know, we had five [special congressional] races up until last week. And of the five races, we won all five. These people back here expected us to lose a couple of those races, maybe more than that. We won. They didn't know what to do.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump ignores two races the Republicans lost, including a high-profile Senate race in Alabama in which Republican Roy Moore lost in an upset to Democrat Doug Jones.
